EditCommand : index = 1

LogicManager --> EditCommand : executes >
EditCommand --> EditPersonDescriptor : contains >
EditCommand ..> ModelManager

EditPersonDescriptor : name = "John Doe"
EditPersonDescriptor : phone = "98765432"
EditPersonDescriptor : email = "johnd@example.com"
EditPersonDescriptor : address = "311, Clementi Ave 2, #02-25"
@enduml
